data.title: monday.com named leader in 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Collaborative Work Management, 3rd time in a row; scored highest on Completeness of Vision and Ability to Execute.
data.description: In New York and Tel Aviv, Israel, monday.com (NASDAQ: MNDY) has been acknowledged as a Leader in the 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Collaborative Work Management (CWM) for the third year in a row. The company was ranked highest for both Completeness of Vision and Ability to Execute out of all vendors assessed in the 2025 report, marking the first instance of monday.com securing the top position on both axes in this evaluation. This recognition showcases the company's continued excellence in the field.
